<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>My Portfolio</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        /* --- CSS VARIABLES & RESET --- */
        :root {
            --bg-color: #0d1117; /* GitHub Dark Dimmed */
            --card-bg: #161b22;
            --text-main: #c9d1d9;
            --text-highlight: #58a6ff; /* GitHub Blue */
            --accent: #238636; /* GitHub Green */
            --border: #30363d;
        }

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            background-color: var(--bg-color);
            color: var(--text-main);
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        a { text-decoration: none; color: inherit; transition: 0.3s; }
        ul { list-style: none; }

        /* --- LAYOUT UTILITIES --- */
        .container {
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }

        section {
            padding: 60px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
        }

        h2 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            color: var(--text-highlight);
        }

        /* --- HERO SECTION --- */
        .hero {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 100px 0;
        }

        .profile-img {
            width: 150px;
            height: 150px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            border: 4px solid var(--text-highlight);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            object-fit: cover;
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 3rem;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .hero p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: #8b949e;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto 30px auto;
        }

        .social-links a {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin: 0 10px;
            color: var(--text-main);
        }

        .social-links a:hover { color: var(--text-highlight); }

        /* --- SKILLS SECTION --- */
        .skills-grid {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 15px;
        }

        .skill-tag {
            background-color: var(--card-bg);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            padding: 8px 16px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        /* --- PROJECTS SECTION --- */
        .project-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .project-card {
            background-color: var(--card-bg);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 20px;
            transition: transform 0.2s;
        }

        .project-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            border-color: var(--text-highlight);
        }

        .project-card h3 { margin-bottom: 10px; }
        .project-card p { font-size: 0.9rem; color: #8b949e; margin-bottom: 15px; }
        
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 5px 10px;
            background-color: var(--accent);
            color: white;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .btn:hover { background-color: #2ea043; }

        /* --- FOOTER --- */
        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 40px 0;
            color: #8b949e;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header class="hero">
        <div class="container">
            <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/150" alt="Profile Photo" class="profile-img">
            
            <h1>[Your Name]</h1>
            <p>Full Stack Developer | Open Source Enthusiast | Tech Writer</p>
            
            <div class="social-links">
                <a href="https://github.com/yourusername"><i class="fab fa-github"></i></a>
                <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/yourusername"><i class="fab fa-linkedin"></i></a>
                <a href="mailto:you@example.com"><i class="fas fa-envelope"></i></a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <section id="about">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>About Me</h2>
            <p>
                Hello! I'm a passionate developer based in [Location]. I love building things for the web. 
                I specialize in creating high-quality websites and applications. When I'm not coding, 
                you can find me [Hobby 1] or [Hobby 2].
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="skills">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>Skills</h2>
            <div class="skills-grid">
                <span class="skill-tag">HTML5</span>
                <span class="skill-tag">CSS3</span>
                <span class="skill-tag">JavaScript</span>
                <span class="skill-tag">Python</span>
                <span class="skill-tag">React</span>
                <span class="skill-tag">Git</span>
                <span class="skill-tag">SQL</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="projects">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>Projects</h2>
            <div class="project-grid">
                
                <div class="project-card">
                    <h3>Project Name 1</h3>
                    <p>A brief description of what this project does and the tech stack used.</p>
                    <a href="#" class="btn">View Code</a>
                </div>

                <div class="project-card">
                    <h3>Project Name 2</h3>
                    <p>A cool automation tool built with Python to scrape data.</p>
                    <a href="#" class="btn">View Code</a>
                </div>

                <div class="project-card">
                    <h3>Project Name 3</h3>
                    <p>A personal dashboard application using React and Firebase.</p>
                    <a href="#" class="btn">View Code</a>
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer>
        <div class="container">
            <p>&copy; 2024 [Your Name]. Built with HTML & CSS.</p>
        </div>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>